          zfswatcher - ZFS pool monitoring and notification daemon

                           version history


version 0.3 released 2013-02-20

 - Disk space usage warnings at configurable thresholds.

 - Experimental FreeBSD and OpenIndiana support.

 - Reconfigure on SIGHUP.

 - Ubuntu ZFS PPA dependency fix.

 - Other minor improvements.


version 0.2 released 2013-02-04

 - Compatibility fix for changes in ZoL 0.6.0-rc14 output formatting.

 - Other minor improvements.


version 0.01 released 2013-02-03

 - Initial release.

